snippet.title: Fe Game Official Launch Trailer – This is Fe
snippet.description:
Explore an extraordinary world of splendor and beauty. Discover the deepest mysteries of the forest. Take wing and protect your home from an encroaching darkness. Become Fe. 
 
Release Date: February 16, 2018.
 
Fe will be available on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC.
 
 Subscribe for more upcoming EA Originals Trailers: https://www.youtube.com/user/EA.
 
Discover more: http://x.ea.com/44800.

Music by Oscar Rydelius and Joel Bille.
